<font color="#666666" face="Verdana, Arial, Sans-serif" size="1">WACKY WEB WEEK<br><br></font>


<font face="Arial,Sans-serif" color="black" size="4"><b>

Summertime and the living is tasty

</b><br></font>
<font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="black" size="1"><br></font>


<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="white" summary="Wacky Web Week">
<tr>
<td width="110" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="FFFFFF">
<a href="http://WindowsSecrets.com/links/btr9udjcuk2td/e3f144h/1i/?url=www.neatorama.com%2F2006%2F06%2F08%2Ftop-10-coolest-bbq-grills"> <img src="http://WindowsSecrets.com/images/wsn/w070412-bbq-grill.jpg" align="left" width="110" height="100" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="3" title="BBQ grill" alt="BBQ grill"></a>
</td>

<td width="510" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="FFFFFF">

<font face="Arial,Sans-serif" color="#000000" size="2">
Summer is coming, and for many folks that means time for a barbecue! Leave it to 
the folks at Neatorama to round up the "Ten Coolest BBQ Grills."<br><br>

The offerings range from gigantic and industrial to artistic stone or ceramic. 
For tailgate parties, there's the Swing-A-Way grill that attaches to the back of 
your truck. For real power, check out the Hemi engine-powered grill whose V8 
engine can roast 240 hot dogs in three minutes.
<a href="http://WindowsSecrets.com/links/btr9udjcuk2td/e3f144h/?url=www.neatorama.com%2F2006%2F06%2F08%2Ftop-10-coolest-bbq-grills" name="ws_wacky web week">
More&nbsp;info</a><br></font>

</td>
